## Usage Notes

- This project is intended for **educational and research purposes**
- **Commercial use** may require additional licensing for BirdNET components
- **Respect local privacy laws** when recording audio
- **Follow wildlife protection regulations** in your area

## Disclaimer

This software is provided for educational and research purposes. Users are responsible for:
- Compliance with local laws regarding audio recording
- Respect for privacy and wildlife protection regulations  
- Proper attribution when using BirdNET AI models
- Understanding that bird identification accuracy may vary